      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5845863685661548792, guid: 43d2733b9089d674882d303d95f64c7e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: introLines.Array.data[0].text
      value: So you're the visitor?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5845863685661548792, guid: 43d2733b9089d674882d303d95f64c7e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: introLines.Array.data[1].text
      value: Go talk to Pellomalou.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5845863685661548792, guid: 43d2733b9089d674882d303d95f64c7e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: introLines.Array.data[2].text
      value: You found it? Good work!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5845863685661548792, guid: 43d2733b9089d674882d303d95f64c7e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: state0Lines.Array.data[0].text
      value: Welcome! Have you talked to Pellomalou yet?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5845863685661548792, guid: 43d2733b9089d674882d303d95f64c7e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: state1Lines.Array.data[0].text
      value: Have you helped Pellomalou?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5845863685661548792, guid: 43d2733b9089d674882d303d95f64c7e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: state2Lines.Array.data[0].text
      value: You helped her? Good work.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5845863685661548792, guid: 43d2733b9089d674882d303d95f64c7e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: state3Lines.Array.data[0].text
      value: Pellomalou told you to help me? That would be great.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5845863685661548792, guid: 43d2733b9089d674882d303d95f64c7e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: state3Lines.Array.data[1].text
      value: Five crosses have been removed from their graves, and the spirits roam
        free, cursing the village.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5845863685661548792, guid: 43d2733b9089d674882d303d95f64c7e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: state3Lines.Array.data[2].text
      value: I need you to find them, and return them, so that the spirits return
        to their graves.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5845863685661548792, guid: 43d2733b9089d674882d303d95f64c7e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: state4Lines.Array.data[0].text
      value: 'You found them? Great work! '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5845863685661548792, guid: 43d2733b9089d674882d303d95f64c7e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: state5Lines.Array.data[0].text
      value: Thank you for saving the village!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5845863685661548792, guid: 43d2733b9089d674882d303d95f64c7e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: genericReminderLines.Array.size
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5845863685661548792, guid: 43d2733b9089d674882d303d95f64c7e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: reminderLines.Array.data[0].text
      value: I told you what to do already.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5845863685661548792, guid: 43d2733b9089d674882d303d95f64c7e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: questDoneLines.Array.data[0].text
      value: You found it? Good work!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5845863685661548792, guid: 43d2733b9089d674882d303d95f64c7e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: introLines.Array.data[0].actorName
